creditline: Gift of funds from Mary and Bob Mersky
dimension: 29 x 20 in. (73.66 x 50.8 cm) (sheet, as printed)
text: This artwork is part of the series COVID-19: Labor Camp Report. Artist's statement on this artwork originally published on the @laborcamp Instagram account: About the endless, nauseating, self-congratulatory proclamations of victory and success. About the lie we live within, where words no longer mean what they used to.
title: May 8, 2020: Victory!
